Perfect! The fix is working correctly. Let me verify by examining the actual implementation:

The fix adds a `.takeUnless` guard before the `.let` block that checks if the enum has no entries:

```kotlin
}?.takeUnless {
    // Do nothing when the enum has no entries
    it.children().none { child -> child.psi is KtEnumEntry }
